  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Cipriani </strong>is open for breakfast and dinner and you'll eat here if you're on half board. Enjoy freshly baked pastries with local jam, cold cuts and cheeses as well as hot options for breakfast. Dinner is a four course buffet of traditional Italian cuisine like homemade pastas, salads and locally-sourced fish. </p>
<p><strong>The Pool Restaurant<span> </span></strong><span>offers a small à la carte menu, with table service, beside the pool (payable locally). </span></p>
<p><strong>The Grill Bar </strong>is the hotels poolside bar. They serve food and drinks, everything from coffee to cocktails. Open seasonally (payable locally). </p>
<p><strong>The American Bar</strong> is a nice place for coffee, light snacks and alcoholic beverages - there's a great cocktail menu. It's located by the garden (payable locally). </p>
<p>Please note that for all restaurants the dress code smart causal, jeans and shorts aren't permitted. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
