  <description><![CDATA[<p>Parc Hotel Gritti is close to the edge of the lake and near the popular Lido Mirabello beach and the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino</a> is close by, just a short walk along the lakeside.</p>
<h2>Down to earth atmosphere</h2>
<p>The hotel offers good value for money and has a down to earth atmosphere, making you feel welcome and comfortable. It has a traditional Italian décor with locally made furniture and antiques. You’ll find everything you need in the rooms – some of them have been renovated recently while others are more traditional.</p>
<h2>Plenty of opportunities to relax</h2>
<p>There's a big garden surrounding the hotel and there are always plenty of shady spots to relax in. The outdoor pool is great on sunny days so make sure you spend some time here. We also love the spa, which has a sauna, Turkish bath and heated indoor pool (some spa facilities are payable locally).</p>]]></description>
